{"tid":1636170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖][多圖] 你地打夠陣地戰未？幾時先識主動反擊？","createTime":"2019-10-07T16:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:58:44.000Z","uid":89898,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"239231e1d8dd8615f2fda3ff3ea395ea4493cfa1","tid":1636170,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"打陣地戰？諗住set晒roadblock有哨有滅煙隊有魔法師就得？對面打一粒彈過嚟就擋一粒彈？跟住呢？睇死你最多咪打到一兩隻狗？然後呢？<br />\n<br />\n你同我睇清楚下面嘅圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KDNWx4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKDNWx4f.png&h=5386da20&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8w3iMpg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8w3iMpg.png&h=7ecc36b6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TyDZvQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTyDZvQX.png&h=9a2ccf9a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XXVtpaY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXXVtpaY.png&h=057dab7e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVOVOCE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVOVOCE.png&h=fd251e43&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9pFfhG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9pFfhG.png&h=bbb0fb79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係，大家唔可以再滿足喺滅到一兩粒彈打到一兩隻狗度。認清楚呢堆傀儡同爪牙背後嘅real enemy。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfwke9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjfwke9m.jpg&h=78d79139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做所有，係所有嘢都同我拉返落呢隻real enemy度。<br />\n<br />\n你要幫美心幫黨鐵裝修嘅，同我至少噴返個有英文嘅tag喺門口（詳見我舊post），最簡單噴「CCP / AntiChinazi」，或者共產黨個斧頭鐮刀symbol。你要貼連儂牆做文宣嘅，再貼多啲中共嘅仆街嘢出嚟，可以貼多啲近期啲貼地啲嘅民生新聞，武漢垃圾廠示威鎮壓、北京勞民傷財賀國慶、豬瘟秋行軍蟲之類。你要打網絡戰線嘅，除咗集中警暴，提返多啲背後嘅大仆街共產黨。你要遊行示威嘅，舉返多啲針對政權嘅標語同口號。<br />\n<br />\n你要明白，共產黨一日有對香港嘅管治權，佢就會無所不用其極咁打壓我地。就算有得一人一票普遍性特首，佢都大可以好似HKTV套選戰咁買起個唔聽話嘅民意代表。<br />\n<br />\n長遠而言要打到呢隻70歲嘅大魔頭，就一定要借外力。個人主張有3條大路線，其實我之後另一個post有講，就係聯臺抗共（另一個中國嘅主權實體）（例如幫手促成臺德建交）、火燒後欄（記住民主中國係手段唔係目標）、圍堵極權（都要多謝班中國人成日喺外國出醜）。<br />\n<br />\nHunger Game入面有句少啲人quote嘅對白，係&quot;Remember who the real enemy is&quot;。中共係我地最大敵人，係文明世界嘅大毒瘤。大家可以咁憎魔警，可唔可以用10倍嘅程度去憎恨佢地背後嘅大魔鬼？應承我即使港雖三戶，亡共必港，得唔得？<br />\n<br />\nTLDR：香港對內要將成個論述轉為對抗中共極權，對外就再集思廣益吓有咩可以做到，中共不倒誓不罷休。"},{"pid":"b8e2e0646c4dbd4c8589a90b8b5c0ce53d91fa5a","tid":1636170,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"唔好再打陣地戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8642fdb5f5e57665222938d84491472e0f04a799","tid":1636170,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"要主動出撃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cab4f083e99474afce3e307e08d72bf90a327af","tid":1636170,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:54:45.000Z","msg":"打死一兩隻傀儡都幫唔到件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d0f532b938ead7a04d94a8897b8b71068b9aa7","tid":1636170,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"何況根本就打唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336ac5b5a84dff6ddbd5a2b02fad4cd545bf2fb3","tid":1636170,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"思維上要升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f2ac4e00b43621b35ca28e0c2a6643ab203c22","tid":1636170,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"論述都要升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29dde43b6d77bc218de913d25f74eff6080c8e4e","tid":1636170,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"香港人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea439a5ae7da7428039cb388f34a9e67748353c","tid":1636170,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:58:16.000Z","msg":"想知連登多唔多共諜就睇呢個post推唔推得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25367687fe47b4e59bd8ebe7b021fdfe6b9dd5c","tid":1636170,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:58:44.000Z","msg":"real enemy冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}